Author: Tony Dewan <tonydewan.com/contact>	
License http://www.opensource.org/licenses/bsd-license.php BSD license, as per the original Minify_CSS class

jsmin 1.1.1
Author: Tony Dewan <tonydewan.com/contact>. Originally by Ryan Grove <ryan@wonko.com>
License http://opensource.org/licenses/mit-license.php MIT License

Curl(9 Dec 2008)
Author: Philip Sturgeon
License: No licence (Free to use)

Compactor 0.6.0
Author: Oliver Lillie (aka buggedcom) <publicmail@buggedcom.co.uk>
Licence: BSD

FEATURES
- Verry simple and lightweight
- Easy to manage
- Verry litte code requierd in the Controllers
- Minification(all whitespace deleted) of all output: JavaScript, CSS and HTML

INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS
1. Copy the files to the /application folder in your CodeIgniter installation
2. Add to config/config.php
//Develepment mode. Values TRUE or FALSE.
//If set to TRUE the output will not be minificated and external assets(CSS and JavaScript) will not be combined for easy debugging.
$config['development_mode'] = true;
